{"tid":2098992,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有無師兄真係反唔落武磊......","createTime":"2020-07-08T02:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T05:41:01.000Z","uid":78243,"like":2,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ea5cf49de95fc1b496ef810a028924306da9f75d","tid":2098992,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:07:52.000Z","msg":"又好波又忠誠，真係反唔落.....<br />\n<br />\n【Now Sports】盛傳受到英超球隊青睞，中國前鋒武磊卻謂：「就算愛斯賓奴降班，我都會留下來。」<br />\n西甲剩下4場聯賽，除非奇蹟出現，相信榜尾的愛斯賓奴難以逃過降班厄運。<br />\n對於傳聞狼隊和屈福特有意斟介，愛斯賓奴前鋒武磊近日接受新華社訪問時回應：「只要球隊仍需要我，我相信有能力繼續作出貢獻，我會選擇留下來。」<br />\n「要避免降班，我們需要全力以赴，在生理和心理上逼使我們自己去到最盡。」前中超神射手武磊今季上陣23場攻入4球，表現未算突出。<br />\n愛斯賓奴現時只有24分，與安全區相差11分之多，極有可能在周三打吡戰後篤定降班。<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=30039095802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D30039095802&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivacrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=aa543ed4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=30039095802</a>"},{"pid":"3bb1207784fdc9db3bae798091dee1e741566a87","tid":2098992,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:09:27.000Z","msg":"召喚會員武磊"},{"pid":"6f99a29f9b3ff1eb2fb27ddac8958eaec70a7206","tid":2098992,"uid":11365,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:10:21.000Z","msg":"踢撚左成季得24分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fb4281a1ac43cfdf1f07c8c26a7f4cdee999bc","tid":2098992,"uid":352454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:10:38.000Z","msg":"23場入得4球<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a67ea8b8e763c7688df0ef2a0f9eefbdc6a0328","tid":2098992,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85fb4281a1ac43cfdf1f07c8c26a7f4cdee999bc","tid":2098992,"uid":352454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:10:38.000Z","msg":"23場入得4球<img src=\"/asset